-- Crescendo Investment, Japan Single-Residence Plan to Merge, Nikkei Reports
-- Fergus Maguire
-- 2010-06-20T21:28:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-20/crescendo-investment-japan-single-residence-plan-to-merge-nikkei-reports.html

          
          
             Crescendo Investment Corp. and Japan
Single-Residence REIT Inc. plan to merge in October to create a
property trust with about 140 billion yen in assets, Nikkei
English News said, without citing anyone.  
 Heiwa Real Estate Co. and Prospect Asset Management Inc.,
the leading shareholders in Crescendo and Japan Single-
Residence, are likely to support the merger, the report said.  
          
          


  


        